	(175,1,'2016-07-03 10:54:06','2016-07-03 10:54:06','[:sr]<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Zent opstaje zahvaljujući velikodušnosti, solidarnosti i podršci svojih čitalaca. Ako možeš pretplati se, poruči, ili doniraj. </span></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Zentu cilj nije profit već pristupačno znanje za sve. Zent je utemeljen u vrednostima zajedništva ali i uverenju da država i državljanstvo nisu njegov nužni medijator. Zent shvata zajedništvo kao prvi od preduslova za ostvarivanje izvan-rednog mesta za sve.</span></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Svojom donacijom podržaćete štampana i online izdanja časopisa, održavanje javnih razgovora i predavanja kao i rad kritičara/ki, teoretičara/ki, umetnika/ca, pisaca i spisateljica.</span></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><br /><br /></p>[:en]<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Zent survives thanks to the generosity, solidarity and support of its readers. If you can please subscribe, purchase, or donate.</span></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Zent does not strive to profit but to offer accessible knowledge for all. Zent is grounded in the values of the common and the conviction that neither the state nor citizenship are its necessary mediators. Zent understands the existence of the common as the first prerequisite for achieving an extra-ordinary place for all.</span></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">With your donation you will support print and online editions of the magazine, organization of public discussions and lectures, as well as the work of independent authors: critics, theorists, artist, and writers.</span></p>[:]','Podrži','','inherit','closed','closed','','37-revision-v1','','','2016-07-03 10:54:06','2016-07-03 10:54:0